00Z","msg":"有，但佢無<br />\n應該係唯一令我想俾一個完整家庭佢嘅人<br />\n其他就算係啲前女友都唔會想放棄自由，甘願受控制於佢<br />\n<br />\n第一眼見就覺得點解依個人咁charm，咁自信，心諗仆街了<br />\n<br />\n後來竟然係佢主動同我講嘢先，仲以為自己有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到認到佢之後就了解到佢一直都係喺脆弱同自信邊緣遊走，自信背後嘅故事<br />\n<br />\n但老實講，除咗佢friendzoned我之外，我同佢性格同生活上唔係太夾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有個衝動想同佢坦誠自己有依個感覺，但真係好不智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f1c049ffffce08055c1ac3c461d7be11bda0ec","tid":1013143,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T19:06:22.000Z","msg":"精蟲上腦就返屋企打飛機啦屌<br />\n一見鍾情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ac359e0e2ebeeb0127d672a6c855c385d5b4ee","tid":1013143,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T19:07:38.000Z","msg":"信 見到靚女都會一見鍾情<br />\n人之常情"},{"pid":"f427cbabfa95711923782ebd718f3fa3d5686a29","tid":1013143,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ec3d63f638e6bb13b723936dbfa9d30644f09c","tid":1013143,"uid":45897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T19:17:57.000Z","msg":"我"}]}